title: Communications Interview
Application Type: I applied online. I interviewed at CO-OP (MA)
Interview Descriptions: Applied online and was contacted to set up an interview. Met with someone from HR and the COO who asked me many questions related to my experience. I was asked what I would do in specific situations.
Interview Questions: Describe how the communications area interacts with recruiting.

title: Speech Language Pathologist Assistant Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 1 week. I interviewed at CO-OP (MA) (Norton, MA) in Jul 2019
Interview Descriptions: I had an in person interview with two women. They asked me many questions, had me prove skills and showed me around. The interview questions were very vague, and the women interviewing me provided no context when asking these questions. They were very rude and looked at me as if they wanted the conversation to be over as soon as possible.
Interview Questions: How do you collect and interpret data?
